videos.description: Greg Summers steals the ball for Navy, leading to a go-ahead 3-pointer by John Carter Jr.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Navy’s Carter Jr. knocks down go-ahead 3) 2019/12/29

videos.headline: Navy's Carter Jr. knocks down go-ahead 3

videos.description: Jay Huff blocks Greg Summers' shot, which leads to an alley-oop slam by Braxton Key to put Virginia on top by five.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Key throws down emphatic alley-oop slam) 2019/12/29

videos.headline: Key throws down emphatic alley-oop slam

videos.description: Kihei Clark lobs it up to Jay Huff who throws down a big-time two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Huff hammers alley-oop slam
